citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:31:33.000Z","msg":"其實相信好多軍營用地係閑置，唔係唔敢用，係根本冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a4cc478c349a25e13f46b00bd6f08eaf704576","tid":643971,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345957369f586929624dd06a0185601e54b7c24b","tid":643971,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49385a498e96ad549efb59a722ac43c52a20b4a2","tid":643971,"uid":111054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T06:08:02.000Z","msg":"哂氣啦，香港政府無權要解放軍交塊地出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T23:03:06.000Z","msg":"而家咪傾囉 你都戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"根據基本法，香港國防外交事務交由中央管理，軍用地屬國防事務，港苦班奴才官員點敢提出丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ef1a281e4e99e445799bfecdf8855a7e89ffb7","tid":643971,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"九龍塘個到噉大都好似冇人用"},{"pid":"9ccee78525c316bb2e36865209543cafbeeaf4ab","tid":643971,"uid":10929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06ef1a281e4e99e445799bfecdf8855a7e89ffb7","tid":643971,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"九龍塘個到噉大都好似冇人用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"咁大個黃金地段真係阻撚住晒"}]}